---

<div class="bg-[#FDF5E9] w-full overflow-hidden text-[#333638] font-poppins">

    <!-- MAIN HEADER -->
    <div class="text-center pt-20 pb-10 px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#D1C1A3] mb-6 italic">
            Crafting Your Legacy in Paradise
        </h1>
        <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
            Your expert luxury destination wedding planner in Colombia. From gourmet catering to exclusive venues in Medellín & Cartagena, we craft bespoke weddings. Plan now.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-10 space-y-16 md:space-y-20">

        <!-- SECTION 1 GROUP: Destination & Intro Text -->
        <div class="space-y-8 md:space-y-12">
            <!-- SECTION 1: Destination (Text Left, Image Grid Right) -->
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 md:gap-16">
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-6">
                     <div>
                         <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#D1C1A3] italic mb-2">
                            Discover the World's Most <br/> Enchanting
                         </h2>
                         <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#4EAC9F] italic">
                            Wedding Destination
                         </h3>
                     </div>
                     <div class="space-y-6 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            Imagine a land where the ordinary creates the extraordinary. A place where emerald mountains kiss the clouds, where colonial cities tell timeless tales of romance, and where the rhythm of life invites you to celebrate with unbridled joy. This is Colombia—a country that has rapidly evolved into one of the world's most coveted locations for luxury destination weddings.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            For the discerning couple, choosing a Colombia destination wedding is a statement of style and sophistication. It is a bold departure from the predictable all-inclusive resort wedding found elsewhere in the Caribbean. Instead, it offers a deeply authentic, culturally rich, and visually stunning experience that lingers in the memory long after the last toast is made. Whether you envision a chic rooftop soirée in the innovative valley of Medellín or a sunset ceremony atop the historic fortifications of Cartagena de Indias, Colombia provides a canvas unlike any other.
                        </p>
                     </div>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                    <!-- Collage Placeholder -->
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 h-full items-center">
                        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-[300px] md:h-[400px]">
                            <Image src={img1} alt="Wedding 1" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-[300px] md:h-[400px] -mt-8 md:-mt-12">
                            <Image src={img2} alt="Wedding 2" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden h-[300px] md:h-[400px]">
                            <Image src={img3} alt="Wedding 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Text Block Full Width (Now closer) -->
             <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center md:text-left md:ml-auto md:mr-0 md:w-1/2 md:pl-8">
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    At Tu San Agustin, we are more than just coordinators; we are your premier luxury destination wedding planner in Colombia. We bridge the gap between your specific vision and the local reality, ensuring that planning a wedding from thousands of miles away feels effortless, transparent, and exciting. We invite you to explore a world where luxury meets warmth, and where your dream wedding becomes a tangible, breathtaking reality.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>


        <!-- SECTION 2: Why Colombia (Text Left, Image Right - Small) -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-12">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#D1C1A3] italic">
                    Why Colombia?
                </h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#4EAC9F] italic mb-4">
                    The Perfect Blend of Exotic and Elite
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    Why are couples from New York, Miami, London, and Madrid flocking to this South American gem? The answer lies in a unique alchemy of world-class infrastructure, incredible value, and stunning biodiversity. Colombia is no longer a hidden secret; it is the rising star of the global wedding industry, offering a sophistication that rivals Lake Como or Napa Valley, but with a vibrant Latin soul that is entirely its own.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:max-w-md md:ml-auto">
                <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg max-h-[250px]">
                    <Image src={img4} alt="Palm trees Colombia" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SECTION 3: Medellin (Image Left - Small, Text Right) -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-12">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:max-w-md order-2 md:order-1">
                <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg max-h-[250px]">
                    <Image src={img5} alt="Medellin venue" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4 order-1 md:order-2">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#D1C1A3] italic">
                    Medellín:
                </h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#4EAC9F] italic mb-4">
                    The City of Eternal Spring
                </h3>
                <div class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                    <p>
                        As a specialized wedding planner in Medellin, we have witnessed the city's transformation into a cosmopolitan hub of innovation, fashion, and warmth. The climate here is our greatest ally—a perpetual spring that allows for open-air events year-round without the oppression of extreme heat or humidity.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        The region boasts spectacular <span class="text-[#4EAC9F]">Colombia wedding venues</span>, ranging from modern architectural marvels in the upscale district of El Poblado to majestic, aristocratic haciendas in the surrounding countryside of Llanogrande and Rionegro. These venues offer a rare combination of privacy and grandeur, surrounded by manicured gardens and rolling hills.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SECTION 4: Cartagena (Text Left, Image Right - Small) -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-12">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#D1C1A3] italic">
                    Cartagena de Indias:
                </h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#4EAC9F] italic mb-4">
                    A Colonial Fairy Tale
                </h3>
                <div class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                    <p>
                        While Medellin offers spring-like elegance, Cartagena brings the heat and history of the Caribbean. For couples dreaming of seaside magic and old-world charm, we offer exclusive access to the city's most coveted spots. Imagine saying "I do" in a 16th-century cathedral, followed by a reception in a restored colonial mansion with balconies overflowing with bougainvillea.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        While Medellin offers spring-like elegance, Cartagena brings the heat and history of the Caribbean. For couples dreaming of seaside magic and old-world charm, we offer exclusive access to the city's most coveted spots. Imagine saying "I do" in a 16th-century cathedral, followed by a reception in a restored colonial mansion with balconies overflowing with bougainvillea.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:max-w-md md:ml-auto">
                <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg max-h-[250px]">
                    <Image src={img6} alt="Cartagena colonial buildings" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SECTION 5: Culinary (Image Left - Small, Text Right) -->
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-12">
