                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#4EAC9F] italic mb-4">
                    Gourmet Wedding Catering
                </h3>
                <div class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                    <p>
                        Food is the heart of any celebration, and in Colombia, it is an art form. Our approach to <span class="text-[#4EAC9F]">gourmet wedding catering</span> goes far beyond standard banquet fare. We believe that the menu should tell a story.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We collaborate with top-tier chefs to design farm-to-table menus that fuse local exotic ingredients—like passion fruit, lulo, artisanal coffee, and Andean tubers—with sophisticated international techniques. Imagine a reception where the food is a conversation starter: interactive ceviche stations, live fire cooking, and dessert tables that look like modern art. This is a sensory journey that delights the palate and honors the destination.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

