        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8 md:gap-12">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#D1C1A3] italic">
                    Unmatched Value for
                </h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#4EAC9F] italic mb-4">
                    High-End Experiences
                </h3>
                <div class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                    <p>
                        One of the most compelling reasons to choose a Colombia luxury wedding planner is the ability to maximize your investment. The favorable exchange rate allows you to access a level of luxury that might be prohibitive in the US or Europe.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        In Colombia, "luxury" is not just a label; it is an abundance of quality found in our all-encompassing <span class="text-[#4EAC9F]">luxury destination wedding packages</span>. We are talking about lavish floral installations using the world's finest export-quality flowers (grown locally), multi-day itineraries involving welcome parties and recovery brunches, and premium entertainment ranging from symphonic orchestras to world-class salsa bands. You are not cutting corners; you are elevating every single aspect of the experience.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:max-w-md md:ml-auto">
                <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg max-h-[250px]">
                    <Image src={img8} alt="Luxury venue interior" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
