                </h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#4EAC9F] italic mb-4">
                    Intimate Luxury
                </h3>
                <div class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                    <p>
                        For those who prefer a more personal celebration, we specialize in high-touch micro-weddings and offer services as a dedicated <span class="text-[#4EAC9F]">elopement planner</span>. Do not mistake these for "small" events; they are concentrated experiences of luxury. We curate intimate settings where every detail is magnified, allowing you to focus on what truly matters: your connection with each other and your closest circle.
                    </p>
                    <p>
