                <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#4EAC9F] italic mb-4">
                    Honoring Tradition
                </h3>
                <div class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                    <p>
                        Executing a religious or cultural wedding abroad requires technical mastery and deep respect for tradition. We are experts in planning a <span class="text-[#4EAC9F]">Jewish wedding</span> in Colombia, handling everything from strict Kosher catering supervision (Mashgiach) to the architectural design of the Chuppah.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We understand the nuances of the timeline, the importance of Shabbat logistics, and the sanctity of your rituals. Whether it is a Persian, Indian, or Jewish traditional ceremony, we have the experience to blend your heritage with the local Colombian flair seamlessly.
