            </h3>
            <div class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-4">
                <p>
                    A destination wedding is not just a five-hour event; it is a three-day vacation for your guests. As your hosts, we take the burden of "tour guide" off your shoulders.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We specialize in Guest Experience Management. This means we coordinate airport transfers, negotiate hotel room blocks at the finest properties, and curate cultural activities. Imagine treating your guests to a private coffee tasting tour, a salsa dancing workshop, or a graffiti tour in Comuna 13. We ensure that your guests' experience is seamless from the moment they land until they depart, turning your wedding into an unforgettable holiday for everyone involved.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SECTION 12: Tu San Agustín Difference (Text Only - Left Aligned) -->
        <div class="md:max-w-2xl space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-poppins font-bold text-[#D1C1A3] italic">
